    "text": "The little person made a bob-curtsey—\"Oh, yes, if you please'm; my name is Mrs. Tiggy-winkle; oh, yes if you please'm, I'm an excellent clear-starcher!\" And she took something out of a clothes-basket, and spread it on the ironing-blanket.",
